Package org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.dtt

Class LNodeTypeAdapter

java.lang.Object
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.SclElementAdapter<DataTypeTemplateAdapter,TLNodeType>
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.dtt.LNodeTypeAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDataTemplate, IDTTComparable<TLNodeType>
public class LNodeTypeAdapter extends SclElementAdapter<DataTypeTemplateAdapter,TLNodeType> implements IDataTemplate, IDTTComparable<TLNodeType>
A representation of the model object LNodeType.

The following features are supported:

  1. Adapter
    • Returns the value of the DataTypeTemplateAdapter reference object
    • Returns the value of the DOAdapter by DO name
  2. Principal functions
    • Add TPrivate under this object
    • Returns the value of the type attribute By DOType Id
    • Returns the value of the id attribute
    • Returns the value of the lnClass attribute
    • Returns ResumedDataTemplate list
  3. Checklist functions
    • Compare Two TLNodeType
    • Check whether TLNodeType contain TDO By Id
